text: Sabina Bajagain (Nepali: सबिना बजगाईं) is a NepalI politician. She is a member of the Koshi Provincial Assembly from Rastriya Prajatantra Party. She was elected via 2022 Provincial Assembly election from Jhapa 1 (B). == References == Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Nepalese politicians
